metadata.description: Welcome to the Wellness Initiative. This project was inspired by the power of positive intentions and affirmations. Affirmations can help you to challenge and overcome self-sabotaging and negative thoughts. And, well, no-one should have self-sabotaging and negative thoughts. This collection will consist of over 10,000 NFT's. Be well!

attributes.value: WI_affirmation_I am powerful, beautiful, brilliant and brave.
